Value: Mighty Kingdom Limited operates as a game developer in Australia. The company develops games for console, PC, and mobile platforms. Its games portfolio includes PETER RABBIT RUN!, AVA'S MANOR, GABBY'S DOLLHOUSE, CONAN CHOP CHOP, SNAP GAMES - SUGAR SLAM, WILD LIFE, LEGO FRIENDS - HEARTLAKE RUSH, SHOPKINS, and DANGER DAYS. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Adelaide, Australia.
